cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the optimization of femtocell networks, which are a type of wireless network. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization algorithms and numerical analysis, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of macrocell users, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
